383
00:34:08,976 --> 00:34:10,318
Tolong tangani secepat mungkin.

384
00:34:25,624 --> 00:34:26,639
Bu Baek.

385
00:34:27,403 --> 00:34:29,692
Apa benar kamu sudah
menentukan tanggal dengan Pak Ban?

386
00:34:30,337 --> 00:34:33,946
