390
00:34:43,421 --> 00:34:44,431
<i>Benar.</i>

391
00:34:44,547 --> 00:34:46,054
Cantik itu kelebihan.

392
00:34:46,127 --> 00:34:48,451
Aku juga mau jadi cantik.

